{"word":"G5268 - ὑποζύγιον - hypozýgion - hoop-od-zoog'-ee-on - Ass","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποζύγιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypozýgion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-od-zoog'-ee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Ass</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கழுதை - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"an ass"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2218 - ζυγός - zygós - dzoo-gos'/2218\">G2218</a>; an animal <i>under</i> the <i>yoke</i> (<i>draught beast</i>), that is, (specifically) a <i>donkey:</i> - ass.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}